      "text": "GeoLink Data Pipeline",
      "fontSize": 95.3333333333333,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GeoLink Data Pipeline",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "buX9-NyD-KkIWhC4N7W3T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 240.66666666666669,
      "y": 311.83333333333326,
      "width": 877.9594116210938,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1740535702,
      "version": 1165,
      "versionNonce": 1998907286,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784419160107,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements:\n - Create groups\n - Expand existing groups over time\n - Users can query groups (and get all corresponding entities as response) by:\n    - Entity ID (and source)\n    - Group ID\n    - Entities Dates Ranges\n - Teams can query groups metrics (and get all corresponding groups IDs as response) by:\n    - Group size\n    - Entities count per source\n    - Total distinct geometries\n    - Distinct geometries count per source \n    - Region\n    - Area range bucket\n    - Bounding Rectangle\n\n---- out of scope ---\n - Create group geometry\n - Join two existing groups\n - Split an existing group with drifting entities\n - Handle points and lines",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements:\n - Create groups\n - Expand existing groups over time\n - Users can query groups (and get all corresponding entities as response) by:\n    - Entity ID (and source)\n    - Group ID\n    - Entities Dates Ranges\n - Teams can query groups metrics (and get all corresponding groups IDs as response) by:\n    - Group size\n    - Entities count per source\n    - Total distinct geometries\n    - Distinct geometries count per source \n    - Region\n    - Area range bucket\n    - Bounding Rectangle\n\n---- out of scope ---\n - Create group geometry\n - Join two existing groups\n - Split an existing group with drifting entities\n - Handle points and lines",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5-obmh2Kfv9qkUpJUmtJz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 241.66666666666674,
      "y": 196.50000000000006,
      "width": 716.759521484375,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 133199894,
      "version": 226,
      "versionNonce": 829721494,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784215283578,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem Definition:\n - Design a data pipeline to ingest geo-spatial data from multiple sources\n   and cluster entities by a given spatial predicate",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem Definition:\n - Design a data pipeline to ingest geo-spatial data from multiple sources\n   and cluster entities by a given spatial predicate",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NxTyIefQUfuT0YSIrVML5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 247.66666666666674,
      "y": 850.1666666666663,
      "width": 591.6795654296875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 121373002,
      "version": 618,
      "versionNonce": 266339850,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784215610152,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-functional Requirements:\n - ~200M entities daily\n - Efficient handling of globally distributed data & hotspots\n - Idempotency of geometries\n - Low latency analytical & user queries < 1s",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-functional Requirements:\n - ~200M entities daily\n - Efficient handling of globally distributed data & hotspots\n - Idempotency of geometries\n - Low latency analytical & user queries < 1s",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
